{"id":14157,"date":"2023-10-20T10:28:00","date_gmt":"2023-10-20T10:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/?p=14157"},"modified":"2023-10-18T11:38:13","modified_gmt":"2023-10-18T11:38:13","slug":"improving-livelihoods-and-banishing-hunger","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/improving-livelihoods-and-banishing-hunger\/","title":{"rendered":"Improving Livelihoods and Banishing Hunger"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Ban Huay Pong is a village of 162 people that has struggled with food security for many years. Much of their farmland has been unusable during the rainy season, meaning farmers miss out on vital land to grow food and improve their livelihoods. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We spoke to Mr Supho who has lived in the village his whole life:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>\u201cWhen I was young, we grew highland rice as we didn&#8217;t have paddies. Now we plant rice in paddies but our irrigation isn&#8217;t good or strong. When the rainy season brings\u00a0 flooding the irrigation dam always must get it repaired. We don\u2019t have enough rice. I graduated from high school and got married when I was 20 years old, and I have 2 children.\u201d\u00a0<\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>When asked about and needs or issues he and other villagers have he told us that they don\u2019t have enough food year round due to the irrigation issues and also not having sufficient water for farming.  Without enough rainfall and then flooding in other months, it is difficult for us to farm all through the year. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"603\" data-id=\"14173\"  src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122508.326.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14173\" srcset=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122508.326.jpg 800w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122508.326-300x226.jpg 300w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122508.326-768x579.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"602\" data-id=\"14172\"  src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122512.230.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14172\" srcset=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122512.230.jpg 800w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122512.230-300x226.jpg 300w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122512.230-768x578.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When asked how the KHT irrigation project has improved his life Mr Suphot said:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> \u201cAfter the project, our life is better. We can get more crops because we have a strong irrigation. That make us can plant in the summer and get more income. Also have enough food for our family\u2026 Our community has a better life. We have time to do other things like spending time with family and friends. We grow more crops and get more income and also have a better well-being. The forest trees increase because we don\u2019t cut down the trees to make nature much better.\u201d\u00a0<\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Our life is better, we have more income. We can grow rice and vegetables to support our children to continue to university for a better life than us. Thank you for supporting us, all the supporters and the KHT team.&#8221;<\/p><p><\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>We are always so proud to hear such positive stories from villagers we have supported, if you would like to support our projects please <a href=\"http:\/\/www.karenhilltribes.org.uk\/donate\">donate<\/a> today!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ban Huay Pong is a village of 162&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":14174,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.12 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Improving Livelihoods and Banishing Hunger - Karen Hilltribes Trust<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/improving-livelihoods-and-banishing-hunger\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Improving Livelihoods and Banishing Hunger - Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Ban Huay Pong is a village of 162...\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/improving-livelihoods-and-banishing-hunger\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2023-10-20T10:28:00+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2023-10-18T11:38:13+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/MicrosoftTeams-image-2023-10-18T122504.989.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"800\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"603\" \/>\n\t<meta 